\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl480\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs28\b0\i0 When applied to these facts, Capital Boost\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s accommodation of Barat\u8217\'92s prayer timing is likely reasonable. As in }{\f0\fs28\b0\i0\ul\ulc0 Toledo}{\f0\fs28\b0\i0 , scheduling adjustments that merely enable the employee to resolve conflicting duties on their own fits the criteria. Permitting prayers during standard breaks while requiring them outside mandatory meetings imposes no substantial burden; neither restriction prevents Barat, with reasonable effort, from fulfilling his five daily prayers within the workday. However, limiting the location of the prayer to the boiler room may result in conflicts Barat can prove to be insurmountable. }}